paleta
________________________________________________________________________________

Change terminal colors on the fly independent of terminal emulator.


requirements
________________________________________________________________________________

+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                                              |
| 1 C99                                                                        |
| 2 POSIX C library                                                            |
|                                                                              |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+


build
________________________________________________________________________________

+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                                              |
| 1 make                                                                       |
| 2 make DESTDIR="" prefix="" install                                          |
|                                                                              |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+


usage
________________________________________________________________________________

+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                                              |
|  Input is [#]000000\\n over stdin in the following order.                    |
|                                                                              |
|     1 <foreground>                                                           |
|     2 <background>                                                           |
|     3 <cursor>                                                               |
|     4 <color0>                                                               |
|     5 <color1>                                                               |
|     6 <color2>                                                               |
|                                                                              |
|       ...                                                                    |
|                                                                              |
|   259 <color256>                                                             |
|                                                                              |
|                                                                              |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+


terminal support
________________________________________________________________________________
          |
       st | no support for 'ESC ] 10;Pt ST', 'ESC ] 11;Pt ST', 'ESC ] 12;Pt ST'.
          | background/foreground are determined based on colors 0 + 15 instead.
          |
alacritty | no issues.
    urxvt | no issues.
      vte | no issues. [0]

[0] all up-to-date vte based terminals.
